### DevTools API Tests
### Tests for DevToolsController endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### OpenCode server: http://localhost:4096

### Get LSP status
### Returns the current Language Server Protocol status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/devtools/lsp
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get formatter status
### Returns the current code formatter status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/devtools/formatter
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Send log message
### Sends a log message to the OpenCode server
POST http://localhost:8080/api/devtools/log
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "service": "test-service",
  "level": "info",
  "message": "Test log message from HTTP client"
}

###

### Send log message with error level
### Sends an error-level log message
POST http://localhost:8080/api/devtools/log
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "service": "test-service",
  "level": "error",
  "message": "Error log message from HTTP client"
}

###

### Send log message with debug level
### Sends a debug-level log message
POST http://localhost:8080/api/devtools/log
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "service": "test-service",
  "level": "debug",
  "message": "Debug log message from HTTP client"
}

###
